{"lastModified":1758554778189,"uri":"c::15746043527::vessel::9520bce0-a0cb-11ee-a424-e7fecd9db876","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Base / Home Port: Spain, South Of France and Italy\nOperating Area: Italy, France, Corsica, Sardinia, Spain, U.S. Virgin Islands, British Virgin Islands, Bahamas, Leeward Islands, Windward Islands\n\nThe 30.48m (100‘0“) luxury performance cruiser L´ Hippocampe (ex. Varsovie) was built by Nautor´s Swan at their Pietarsaarishipyard in Finland in 2008. She is a pedigree sailing yacht with an elegant interior and exterior design by a revered design house German Frers. In 2023, she underwent an extensive technical refit and is now in top-tier condition, ready to take her charter guests on new sailing adventures in comfort and style. L´ Hippocampe was built to be easy to sail and offers excellent sail handling. The yacht easily reaches speeds of 10 knots+ and regularly achieves 240 miles of sailing in a day. Modified from the Swan 100S version features a coach roof raised at the front, giving additional forward-facing salon windows and an additional 5in of headroom in the engine room.","blueprint":{"name":"L'HIPPOCAMPE","images":["/media/media::image::c::15746043527::vessel::9520bce0-a0cb-11ee-a424-e7fecd9db876::assets::f5e85280-a0cc-11ee-a424-e7fecd9db876.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::15746043527::vessel::9520bce0-a0cb-11ee-a424-e7fecd9db876::assets::f5eb5fc0-a0cc-11ee-a424-e7fecd9db876.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::15746043527::vessel::9520bce0-a0cb-11ee-a424-e7fecd9db876::assets::f5ea7560-a0cc-11ee-a424-e7fecd9db876.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::15746043527::vessel::9520bce0-a0cb-11ee-a424-e7fecd9db876::assets::f5e9d920-a0cc-11ee-a424-e7fecd9db876.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::15746043527::vessel::9520bce0-a0cb-11ee-a424-e7fecd9db876::assets::f5eac380-a0cc-11ee-a424-e7fecd9db876.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::15746043527::vessel::9520bce0-a0cb-11ee-a424-e7